## Evidence sharing rules XML samples

You can download the following sharing rules XML samples that provide guidelines for using the sharing rules XML schema to map logically equivalent evidence types in Social Program Management.

- [Sample Logically Equivalent Evidence XML Sharing Rules](/samples/SampleLogicallyEquivalentConfigurations_8000_Refresh.zip)

Note, the sharing rules XML samples were last refreshed in Social Program Management 8.0.0.

For more information about configuring logically equivalent evidence, see the *Evidence Broker Guide*.
